{"type": "article", "id": 26220, "title": "Valentino 将调整亚洲区价格，JohnnyDepp 女儿登杂志封面｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-04-29T10:40:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 26970, "name": "调整价格"}, {"id": 70, "name": "财报"}, {"id": 26971, "name": "季度收益"}, {"id": 23146, "name": "杂志封面"}, {"id": 26972, "name": "纹身贴纸"}, {"id": 10486, "name": "平底鞋"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 3112, "name": "Bally"}, {"id": 16950, "name": "Columbia"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 1466, "name": "Hermès"}, {"id": 26973, "name": "Grace Coddingto"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133101CcHWqLneFGiRJBvX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/tiffany-grace-coddington-creative-partner-10419799-10419799/\"><b>Vogue 前时尚总监任 Tiffany 创意职位</b></a>｜一月从 Vogue 离职后，Grace Coddingto 和 Comme des Garçons 合作推出了自己的香水，最新的动向是，Tiffany &amp; Co. 聘用她担任“创意合作伙伴”，这是 Tiffany 首次设置这一职位，Tiffany 还透露她正在为品牌筹备秋季广告，将在九月刊的时尚、奢侈、旅行及生活方式出版物上展示。<br></p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/business/valentino-price-realignment-asia-10420306/\">Valentino 一季度收益上涨 9.4%，将调整亚洲价格</a></b>｜罗马时装品牌 Valentino 周四发布财报，显示一季度的持续增长，继去年超过 10 亿的营收后，今年的一季度上涨了 9.4% 至 2.56 亿欧元（约合 2.89 亿美元）。并表示将从 4 月 29 日开始在大中华和东南亚地区调整价格，以减少与欧洲之间的价格差异。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/hermes-leather-goods-luxury-hermes-10420063/\"><b>爱马仕除皮具及马具外，整体收益下滑</b></a>｜爱马仕（Hermès ）近日发布的财报显示，截至 3 月 31 日的一季度，除了皮具以及马具部门外，其全产品线收益下滑。皮具类上涨了 15.5%，而丝绸和纺织品下跌了 9.5%，香水减少了 3.5%，腕表减少 3.3%，成衣和时尚配件下跌 2.3%，珠宝和家居则下滑了 2.6%。爱马仕季度销售额有 6.1% 的增长，至 11.9 亿欧元（约合 13.1 亿美元）。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/columbia-sportswear-sales-earnings-10420713/\"><b>Columbia Sportswear 一季度销售额破纪录</b></a>｜Columbia 运动装近日宣布一季度销售额破纪录且收益超出预期。截至 3 月 31 日的一季度净收益增长了 20% 至 3180 万美元胜预期。销售额则增长了 10% 至 5.251 亿美元，同样破集团一季度销售额纪录，超出 FactSet 4.94 亿的预期。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/menswear-news/designer-luxury/berluti-germany-frankfurt-10420653-10420653/\"><b>Berluti 德国开第一家店</b></a>｜法国品牌 Berluti 在德国开第一家店，位于法兰克福 Goethestrasse  大街。5942 平方英尺的精品店内售卖 Berluti 的鞋履、皮具和成衣，店内很多装修细节采用了品牌标志性的威尼斯皮革，如扶手椅、墙面和地板。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133043ORGv4CZUrithlaEj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021330438d6kxZ5spCbNEI9f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133044VY27QWBks8IlUXNP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Johnny Depp 女儿 Lily-Rose Depp 登上法国版 <i>Vanity Fair</i> 杂志封面：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133044FDVpX546PrfS2CMn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133045YynolMeSEaT5m0Bk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133045f0mMosdhrykCWJZQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133046YFGO9aj6ZQKnVu8d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021330462tODmKGC5xI4fB3g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/hm-summer-2016-campaign/\">H&amp;M 发布夏日泳装系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213304761a7p84zOtev9QcF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133047fZxBEPSGAvKuWw86.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021330472d56FJpelEvVyH1L.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133048fxgsei3EOZUo6R0L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133048FOLo4lpz305fn1NQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133049W8Fc0kEGwV1bgn2a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133049Hc5XVMZojsYrTgaC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133050JgQ694NTiZvFqxMS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://bae.hypebeast.com/2016/4/nike-tech-hypermesh-ss16-collection\">Nike 全新 Tech Hypermesh 系列</a>，包括男装风行者夹克和女装背心式的外套，应对夏季变化多端的天气，纺织面料防风，网眼部分则是为了加强通风透气效果，将在 5 月 5 日上市。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133050cQ8RFdoCnaX2EuK5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133051bxqtQuI0GeLURX4N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021330526UBND4x2VRus0LYM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133052VhbFqZgj2WJQUkMc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133053DIQWPcsEiKyXzM4C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133053ujOkUTrDcYX4EdN0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/burberry-2016-make-up-collection-london-with-love/\">Burberry 夏日彩妆系列 London with Love</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021330547QSBw5qg0lI4dJab.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133054A1UjR46z0vLBCZoa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133055yqWuCafJOInBlRpd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">时装品牌们的 2016 秋季系列有哪些不错的平底、低跟鞋：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021330563bRZ2sDkBPEm0j1o.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Rene Caovilla</p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133056Hyu5APFm6CRoLl3S.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Chanel</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133057S2v1WpuT0GUdc8HQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Manolo Blahnik</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133057XMRPl2nOSUz0Jtpr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Kate Spade</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133057hXu3klUHajDAvdM6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Alexandre Birman</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021330583zYcEdMIhR42iQAX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Paula Cademartori</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133058sSmpXdTjfC8GkbDB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Theory</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133059yi5drxnfSEpPBY1m.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Bally</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">超模 Alessandra Ambrosio 曾设计过自己的泳装及服饰系列，今年她的  <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/alessandra-ambrosio-body-art-flash-tattoos/\">Ale by Alessandra 产品线将新增人体艺术类别</a>，即纹身贴纸：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133059MWPZ0UKbjcNumE2O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133100QzHwCGIj20JsXZkB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.36125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133100dcAR69wVHQlt20qC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}